<div class="general-wrapper">
  <div class="portfolio-wrapper">
    <div class="container projects-container">
      <div class="row header-row">
        <h1>My portfolio</h1>
      </div>
      <figure class="row project-row cap-right" id="inline">
        <figcaption>
          <div>
            <h3>InLine</h3>
            <p>Description of the InLine project. This project took around 3 weeks from start to finish and I was responsible for the whole stack.</p>
            <p>The idea of the application is to digitize physical queuing systems in various B2C businesses, thus giving consumers and clients more time to spend as they wish.</p>
            <p>Technologies used: Ruby on Rails, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, ActionCable, SQL, ActiveRecord, PostgreSQL, Heroku.</p>
            <a href="https://inline-app.com" target="_blank"><p>https://inline-app.com</p></a>
            <a href="https://github.com/charliejeppsson/inline" target="_blank"><p>https://github.com/charliejeppsson/inline</p></a>
          </div>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="row project-row cap-right" id="unify">
        <figcaption>
          <div>
            <h3>Unify</h3>
            <p>Description of the Unify project. This project took 10 days from start to finish and it was created in a group of 4 during Le Wagon's full stack coding bootcamp in Barcelona the summer of 2017.</p>
            <p>The idea of the application is to create the Happn for the professional network.</p>
            <p>Technologies used: Ruby on Rails, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, ActionCable, SQL, ActiveRecord, PostgreSQL, Heroku.</p>
            <a href="https://uni-fy.eu" target="_blank"><p>https://uni-fy.eu</p></a>
            <a href="https://github.com/charliejeppsson/rails-unify" target="_blank"><p>https://github.com/charliejeppsson/rails-unify</p></a>
          </div>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="general-wrapper">
  <div class="connect-wrapper">
    <div class="container connect-box">
      <div class="row header-row">
        <h1>Connect with me</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="row" style="margin: 30px;">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3">
          <form action="http://formspree.io/charlie.jeppsson1@gmail.com" method="post">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="name">Your name:</label>
              <input name="form-name-input" type="text" name="name" class="form-control" placeholder="Elon Musk" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Your email address:</label>
              <input type="email" name="_replyto" class="form-control" placeholder="elon.musk@gmail.com" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="body">Your message:</label>
              <textarea name="body" class="form-control" rows="4" placeholder="Dear Charlie..." required></textarea>
            </div>
            <button class="btn btn-basic btn-block" class="form-control">Submit</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

